      "createdAt": "2024-03-21T08:10:44.454Z",
      "author": "Matias.Monday (Matias)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello there <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/bolt\">@Bolt</a> and welcome to the community!</p>\n<p>I hope you like it here <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/muscle.png?v=12\" title=\":muscle:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":muscle:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>As of today, there is no way to get a webhook when someone writes in that search box. It is also not possible to query for the data the user inputs there.</p>\n<p>You can create a feature request <a href=\"https://community.monday.com/c/developers/api-feature-requests/58\">here</a>, or if you want, I can turn this topic into a request <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/grin.png?v=12\" title=\":grin:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":grin:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Cheers,<br />\nMatias</p>"
    }
